  <summary>5/9/2001--Introduced.
Authorizes the Secretary of Agriculture to provide assistance (replanting assistance and/or seedlings) to eligible commercial orchardists and tree farmers who have suffered qualifying tree losses caused by a natural disaster.Makes such provision applicable to losses incurred after January 1, 2000.</summary>
